00:12:37,953 --> 00:12:40,995
And lots of indie games, for this reason,

259
00:12:41,755 --> 00:12:44,657
use a distinctive art style or distinctive key art

260
00:12:45,037 --> 00:12:48,100
to stand out from everything else out there.

261
00:12:49,771 --> 00:12:51,252
And here's a really important point.

262
00:12:51,952 --> 00:12:54,654
You don't have to spend a lot of money

263
00:12:54,914 --> 00:12:56,254
to find something distinctive.

264
00:12:56,294 --> 00:12:57,855
Again, leading to your limitations.

265
00:12:58,496 --> 00:13:00,056
Sometimes you do, sometimes you can.

266
00:13:00,097 --> 00:13:01,657
Some games need to be beautiful

267
00:13:01,717 --> 00:13:03,598
and need to look like all the money that was spent on them.

268
00:13:04,479 --> 00:13:09,442
But here is, this is Rineira, one of our cultist acolytes.

269
00:13:10,122 --> 00:13:12,983
