320
00:15:22,972 --> 00:15:24,092
we get a rush of people who,

321
00:15:27,528 --> 00:15:29,690
haven't heard about the game through word of mouth,

322
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:31,271
haven't been recommended by a friend,

323
00:15:32,012 --> 00:15:33,834
and many of them don't know what they're getting into

324
00:15:33,974 --> 00:15:36,576
and react with confusion, dismay, or anger.

325
00:15:36,596 --> 00:15:39,259
