1263
01:00:14,298 --> 01:00:17,862
who likes short, concise, pithy text,

1264
01:00:18,442 --> 01:00:21,085
then cards are great because they give you a natural limit

1265
01:00:21,826 --> 01:00:22,526
to write to.

1266
01:00:24,429 --> 01:00:31,037
And also, if you are working on very low budgets, cards are great, because to add content to the game,

1267
01:00:31,257 --> 01:00:35,522
you add some text, you add some behavior, and you add a little image.

1268
01:00:36,703 --> 01:00:41,689
